== Abakɔsem ne afarebae ==
Jollof fi Senegambian mamtamu a  Wolof or Jolof Empire dii won so14th century mu, endɛ [[Senegal]], The Gambia ne [[Mauritania]], a wɔ dua ɛmoo. Aduane no fi ammanmere aduane bi a yɛ frɛ no  thieboudienne, a yɛ de ɛmoo, nsuomu nam, nsuomu nam a nwora hyɛ ho ne nhaban ayɛ. Aduane ne kuadwuma mu abakɔsemkafo  James C. McCann ka sɛ ɛmoo fi upper Niger valley, nanso ɔngye ndi sɛ aduane yi terɛɛ fi Senegal kɔ sii bebiara a edu ndɛ efisɛ ɔnhu ɔkwan a ɛbɛ tumi aterɛ saa wɔ "kasahodoɔho nimdepɛ, abakɔsem anaa amanyɔsem mu". Na ɛmom ɔkaa sɛ aduane no trɛɛ wɔ  Mali empire, ne titirew ne  Djula adetɔnfo  a wɔn hyeta wiase mbia beberee a wɔ tɔn ade wɔ kuro kese mu, nketewa ne bebiara a wɔ di ɛmoo ho dwa ne  Nkremo. Marc Dufumier, Emeritus twerɛtwerɛ payin ma ɔkwan a wɔ de abɔdemu nyansapɛ ne abɛfo ne ndua yɛ kuadwuma su su bɛbi a aduane yi fi sɛ ɛnam nsusansoɔ a fi ɔkwan a abrɔfo na wo di yen so no fa so bɔ nkate dua ho dawuro wɔ Senegal mfimfinii ma French ngo adwuma no, ne bɛ bi a wɔ te te atoko ne sorghum aduane ahoro di so no ma wɔ de ɔhyɛ kraa ɛmoo a ebubu fri  Anaafoɔ apueɛ mamtamu wɔ Asia. Ɛno na ɛterɛyɛ wɔ abakɔsem adetɔn, ammamerɛ ne ɔsom kwan so ka Senegal bɔ Gana, Nigeria ne aman ahoro mu ko si endɛ, te sɛ  Tijāniyyah Sufi fekuo a ɛde amanfoɔ mpempem efi Abibirem Atɔeɛ kɔ Senegal afi afi no.

== Asaase ho ntentensoɔ ne nsesayɛ ==
Jollof yɛ aduane a agye din wɔ Abibirem atɔeɛ. Yɛ wɔ mamtamu nsesayɛ wɔ din ne neɛma a wɔ nua ,  wɔ  Mali wɔ frɛ no ''zaamè'' wɔ  Bamanankan. Aduane ne din a yɛ frɛ no  Jollof no fri  Wolof foɔ,din mu,ɛmom wɔ Senegal ne Gambia no, wɔ frɛ Wolof sɛ ''ceebu jën'' anaa ''benachin''. Wɔ aman a wɔ ka french kasa no ,wɔ frɛ no  ''riz au gras''. En sesayɛ no nyinaa akyi no , aduane no wɔ "pɛmesibea baakɔ" wɔ mamtamu ahoro nyinaa na ɛyɛ aduane a ɛwɔ Abibirem ha a agye din wɔ Abibirem asaasetam abɔnten so .

== Neɛma a wɔ de yɛ ==
[[File:Fried_Rice,_Jollof_rice_and_salad,_served_with_Grilled_Chicken.jpg|thumb|ɛmoo a yɛ de nhaban afra akye, jollof ɛmoo ne nhaban ahoro,a yɛde akokɔ  nam aka ho .]]
Jollof ɛmoo wɔ ammamere mu no yɛ, ɛmoo, angwa, atɔsodeɛ te sɛ ntosu,gyeene,mɛko kɔkɔɔ.garlic, akakaduro ne meko a ano yɛ den.  Sɛ neɛ aduane no ahosuo no bɛ yɛ fɛ nti, wɔ de ntosu a ɛwɔ konkomu ka ho. Neɛma a wɔ de ka ho ma no yɛ dɛ ne nkyen,magi, nutmeg,ne nhaban te sɛ rosemary, nketenkete ne nea ɛke ka ho,ne  curry powder . Sɛ nea aduane no be di mu nti , wɔ de akokɔ nam , kurokuro nam,nantwi nam, aponkye nam ne nsuomu na ka ho.

== Mamtamu nsonosonoyɛ ne kuratwe ==
Aman a ɛwɔ Abibirem atɔeɛ mamtamu nyinaa wɔ biribi soronko a ɛmɛ aduane no da nso, Wɔ [[Ghana|Gana]], [[Alata man|Nigeria]], [[Sierra Leone]], [[Liberia]] ne  [[Cameroon]] si akan wɔ nea ne jollof yɛ dɛ ho. Aman a ɛhyɛ mu kena ne  Nigeria ne Gana,  wa to ne din sɛ Jollof kuratwe ".

'''Nigeriafo Jollof'''

Ɛwɔ mu sɛ nsronsronyɛ da aduane nyinaa mu, neɛma a Nigeriafo de yɛ wɔn jollof no ne ɛmoo atenten, ntosu ne ntosu a ɛwɔ konko mu,meko, angwagyeene,ne magi.  Yɛ nua neɛma no beberee wɔ kyensen baako mu, a meko ne ntosu a ya yam na edi kan. Ɛno ben ansa yɛ de nsuo ne ɛmoo no agu mu ma na ben. Aduane no ben a na yɛ de enam aka ho edi. Nnipa bi nso kye brodeɛ a abere ka ho, anaa moi moi, atɔsodeɛ a ya nua anaa sɛ nea yɛ twetwa ne nea ɛke ka [https://food52.com/recipes/61557-classic-nigerian-jollof-rice]

Ɛwɔ bia a nsutene da wɔ Nigeria no a nsumunam na agye din wɔ hɔ no, nsumunam na wɔ de di aduane no.

Wɔ de atɔsodeɛ angwa, gyeene, meko akɛse no, garlic, meko a ano yɛ ya, ntosu a ɛwɛ konko mu, nantwi anaa  aponkye anaa akokɔ nam ne Gana ɛmoo anaa amanɔne deɛ na ɛyɛ Gana jollof, ne meko tumtum. Sɛ wɔ nua aduane no a, wɔ di kan nua enam no na wakye. Wɔ kye nam no wie a na wɔ de neɛma no aka no agu mu kyense no mu anua ma na ben ansa wɔ de ɛmoo no agu mu anua ma na ben. Wɔ de aponkye, akokɔ , nsuo mu nam anaa nantwi nam anaa atɔsodeɛ na edi Gana jollof .

Wɔ de [[Meko|shito]] nso de Gana jollof, (shito yɛ meko bi a efi Gana) ne atɔsodeɛ wɔ abere a wɔ de dwumadie bi wɔ Gana,.

== Edingye wɔ wiase afanaa nyinaa ==
Fi ti afe 2010 mu no,amanfo bebree a ɛwɔ amanɔne aniagye aduane a ɛwɔ Abibirem atɔeɛ ho. Wa hyehyɛ jollof aduane ho [[afahyɛ]] wɔ  Washington, DC, wɔ Amereka , ne Toronto, Canada. "Wɔ di Jollof da wɔ wiase afanaa nyinaa" fi Ɔsanaa bosome no da ɛtɔ so eduonu mienu wɔ afe 2015 mu ko si endɛ, na agye din wɔ  abɛɛfo ntentan nyinaa so.

